    "name": "Maki: Paw of Fury",
    "steam_appid": 2119850,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119850/extras/dfaa277819d1ee2d2846f0f2f44e8fc3.poster.avif?t=1736252610\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119850/extras/dfaa277819d1ee2d2846f0f2f44e8fc3.webm?t=1736252610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119850/extras/dfaa277819d1ee2d2846f0f2f44e8fc3.mp4?t=1736252610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MAKI: PAW OF FURY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Maki是一款以复古街机宝石风格的精美动画格斗游戏。利用您的武术技能昏迷和击败对手并踢主要小人的屁股！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >愤怒的爪子</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您会像一只甜美的小狐狸一样玩耍。不要被他的可爱而愚弄，他研究了Tsume No Ken的艺术，他是一位出色的战士！他现在必须从邪恶的马普手中救出他的朋友。在这项任务中，他不仅可以通过拳头的力量来帮助他，而且还可以通过他最喜欢的菜……武器得到帮助。金枪鱼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119850/extras/28d7f8923092dd1d60c865777d9d322a.poster.avif?t=1736252610\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119850/extras/28d7f8923092dd1d60c865777d9d322a.webm?t=1736252610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119850/extras/28d7f8923092dd1d60c865777d9d322a.mp4?t=1736252610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >街机爱</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maki：Fury的Paw是由阿根廷Studio Bacord开发的游戏。这是一个由经典街机游戏的爱好者制定的项目，这是对美好时光的致敬和战斗机的排队。所有这些都带有幽默和美丽的视觉效果和音乐。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119850/extras/e1444c3f55822cb5978e8bcb86efbe7e.poster.avif?t=1736252610\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119850/extras/e1444c3f55822cb5978e8bcb86efbe7e.webm?t=1736252610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119850/extras/e1444c3f55822cb5978e8bcb86efbe7e.mp4?t=1736252610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >斗争！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越五个独特的地点！每个级别都是不同的，每个级别都有一个独一无二的迷你游戏。独自面对多元化和危险的对手，或者在沙发合作模式下与朋友面对！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在道场练习您的技能和运动，并准备克服困难的老板。这是时间……战斗！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主要特征：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >好，古老，复古风格的游戏玩法</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >美丽的视觉和大气音乐</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与之战斗的15种以上类型的敌人</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可爱的可玩角色：Maki和Tincho</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >金枪鱼作为强大的武器</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
